name: Poppies on Grey - 24 x 24 Print on Canvas
description:
Adorn your walls with this vibrant painting of poppies for a fresh pop of color!  A 24" x 24" printed canvas.

This print is custom made through partnership with Green Box Art out of San Diego. They print the image of my painting with the giclée printing method to achieve optimum clarity and color resolution, printing onto an artist’s grade premium canvas. Each piece is hand-stretched over a 1 ½” deep all-natural wood frame. The canvas wraps around the sides providing a finished decorative edge.  Each piece arrives ready to hang in your home.
